<p><font size="1">88. Quoted in Joseph and Dole, <i>op. cit., </i>note
56, pp. 14-15.</font> </p>

<p><font size="1">89. See Gerald Davidson, <i>Hrgs., </i>pp.
326-27.</font> </p>

<p><font size="1">90. See material in <i>Second Meth. Conf. and
