<p><font size="1">9 1. Kramer, <i>Hrgs., </i>pp. 668-69.</font> </p>

<p><font size="1">92. Goldstein 1970, p. 35.</font> </p>

<p><font size="1">93. John Langrod, &quot;Secondary Drug Use
